:: Gwylan Talk Clothes Intro
<<effects>><<run statusCheck("Gwylan")>>
<<set $gwylanSeen.pushUnique("clothes_intro")>>

<<if $location is "forest_shop">>
	<<switch $speech_attitude>>
		<<case "meek">>
			"This shop is cosy, but a little strange," you say. "It's like a big maze."
		<<case "bratty">>
			"What's with this place?" you ask. "It's cute, but I can't keep track of anything here."
		<<default>>
			"Why is your shop like this?" you ask. "It's homely, but it's so hard to keep track of anything."
	<</switch>>
<<else>>
	<<switch $speech_attitude>>
		<<case "meek">>
			"Your shop is cosy, but strange," you say. "It's like a big maze."
		<<case "bratty">>
			"What's with your shop?" you ask. "It's cute, but I can't keep track of anything there."
		<<default>>
			"Why is your shop so strange?" you ask. "It's homely, but it's so hard to keep track of anything there."
	<</switch>>
<</if>>
<br><br>

<<if _gwylanStatus.includes("cautious")>>
	<<His>> head tilts as <<he>> looks you up and down. <<His>> eyes linger on the left side of your chest for just a moment, before looking back up and smiling at you.
<<else>>
	<<He>> smiles at you.
<</if>>
"If you come around enough, you'll get used to it. If you think about what you're looking for hard enough, you might get an idea of how you can find it." <<He>> pauses to look you over<<if $auriga_scar gte 1>> again<</if>>.
<br><br>

"For everything you do find, there must be a story to match, so when you find something interesting..." <<He>> leans forward. "<span class="teal">Come tell me about it!</span>
Even if it's unpleasant. <i>Especially</i> if it's unpleasant. You shouldn't keep such things to yourself."
<br><br>

<<gwylanOptions>>

:: Gwylan Talk Clothes Error
<<effects>><<run statusCheck("Gwylan")>><<set _clothesTalk to $clothesBeingTalkedAbout>><<unset $clothesBeingTalkedAbout>>
You go to show Gwylan the <<print setup.specialClothesSets[_clothesTalk].text>>, but there's nothing there.
<br><br>

Something's gone wrong. There's a hole in the world in the shape of the clothes you were just holding.
<span class="red">You have a feeling that you should tell some higher power about this clear bug in reality.</span>
You should tell them that the '<<print setup.specialClothesSets[_clothesTalk]>>' set was not found in the forest shop.
<br><br>

Gwylan gives you a look of concern. "Are you feeling alright? You look a little dizzy." <span class="red">Your sense of control shatters</span>, but only for a moment. <<lcontrol>><<gcontrol>>
<br><br>

<<gwylanOptions>>

:: Gwylan Talk Clothes Cheated
<<effects>><<run statusCheck("Gwylan")>><<set _clothesTalk to $clothesBeingTalkedAbout>><<unset $clothesBeingTalkedAbout>>
<<set $gwylanSeen.pushUnique("clothes_talk_cheated")>>
You show Gwylan the <<print setup.specialClothesSets[_clothesTalk].text>>, and try to make up a story to go along with it.
<br><br>

<<He>> rests <<his>> head in <<his>> hand and looks bored. "You don't need to lie to me. <span class="pink">I'm only interested in stories that actually happened.</span> Come back and show me again when you've got some real experiences to share."
<br><br>

<span class="pink">It seems there's no use in showing off anything that you didn't earn.</span>
<br><br>

<<gwylanOptions>>

:: Gwylan Talk Clothes Bypassed
<<effects>><<run statusCheck("Gwylan")>><<set _clothesTalk to $clothesBeingTalkedAbout>><<unset $clothesBeingTalkedAbout>>
<<set $gwylanSeen.pushUnique("clothes_talk_bypassed")>>
You show Gwylan the <<print setup.specialClothesSets[_clothesTalk].text>>, and try to remember how you found it. You pause. The memory is foggy.
<br><br>

You think harder. The memory feels alien, as if it was something you experienced...
<br><br>

"...in another life?" Gwylan finishes your thought before you can speak it. <<Hes>> looking at you intently. "Like a memory you know you never lived through, but you can just barely remember regardless? A memory with no name to match?"
<br><br>

You nod. <<He>> looks fascinated. "I've had such moments myself. Like when I..." <<He>> stops <<himself>> as <<he>> looks you over. "Never mind, it's likely just déjà vu. <span class="blue">Maybe if you try to re-enact those memories, it'll clear up.</span> Come tell me all about it when you do!"
<br><br>

<span class="blue">It seems there's no use in showing off anything that you don't have your own stories for.</span>
<br><br>

<<gwylanOptions>>

:: Gwylan Talk Clothes Savescum
<<effects>><<run statusCheck("Gwylan")>><<set _clothesTalk to $clothesBeingTalkedAbout>><<unset $clothesBeingTalkedAbout>>
<<set $gwylanSeen.pushUnique("clothes_talk_savescum")>><<run localStorage.setItem("gwylanTalk", "seen")>>
You show Gwylan the—
<br><br>

"Stop," <<he>> says, holding a hand up. <<His>> smile is bittersweet. "<<pcPetname "Gwylan" "simple">>...
<<if $gwylanSeen.includes("yearning")>>
	are you so desperate to spend time with me?"
<<else>>
	does your thirst for knowledge know no bounds?"
<</if>>
<br><br>

You frown. "What are you talking about? I just want to ask about the <<print setup.specialClothesSets[_clothesTalk].text>>."
<br><br>

"And many others, I'm sure." Gwylan closes <<his>> eyes. "Indulgence is a danger you must always be wary of. Those who would devour anything put in front of them, without giving time to recover, will find themselves in a barren home with barren crops... and they too will, inevitably, starve."
<br><br>

<<His>> eyes open again, and lock on yours. "You need not gorge yourself on your curiosity. This is not a choice I can make for you, but <span class="lblue">please, pace yourself. Take time to stop and smell the roses.</span> I'll still be here tomorrow, I promise."
<br><br>

<<gwylanOptions>>

<!-- Holidays -->

:: Gwylan Talk Clothes Halloween
<<effects>><<run statusCheck("Gwylan")>>
You browse all the Halloween costumes around the shop, finding each one easily.
<br><br>

<<if $worn.upper.name.includes("witch dress") and $worn.lower.name.includes("witch skirt")>>
	<<He>> points at the witch costume you're wearing. "I think there's something wrong with the fit on yours. Would you mind posing for me?"
	<br><br>

	<<link [[Pose for Gwylan (0:20)|Gwylan Talk Clothes Halloween 2]]>><<pass 20>><<set $phase to 1>><</link>>
	<br>
<<else>>
	"Hey, could you bring that dress here for a moment?" <<he>> asks, pointing to one of the witch costumes. You oblige, and <<he>> holds the dress and hat up in front of you.
	<br><br>

	"I think there's something wrong with the fit. Would you mind trying it on for me?"
	<br><br>

	<<link [[Try it on for Gwylan (0:20)|Gwylan Talk Clothes Halloween 2]]>><<pass 20>><<set $phase to 0>><</link>>
	<br>
<</if>>
<<link [[Do not|Gwylan Talk Clothes Halloween No]]>><</link>>
<br>

:: Gwylan Talk Clothes Halloween 2
<<effects>><<run statusCheck("Gwylan")>><<set $daily.gwylan.clothesTalk++>>
<<set $gwylanTalked.pushUnique("halloween")>>

<<if $phase is 1>>
	<<handheldundress "gwylan_clothes_halloween">><<handheldwear "broomstick">>
	You hunch over and palm your hands to your nose as if you're plotting something.
	<<if !$worn.head.name.includes("witch hat")>>
		<<set $hatGiven to true>>
		<<headundress "gwylan_clothes_halloween">>
		<<if $worn.upper.name is "gothic witch dress">>
			<<headwear "gothic witch hat" "black" "green">>
		<<else>>
			<<headwear "witch hat" "black" "green">>
		<</if>>
		A witch hat is dropped on your head to complete the look, briefly obscuring your vision. You lift it to see Gwylan inspecting you, <<his>> hand to <<his>> chin.
	<<else>>
		Gwylan inspects you, <<his>> hand to <<his>> chin.
	<</if>>
<<else>>
	<<undress "gwylan_clothes_halloween">><<upperwear "witch dress" "black" "green">><<headwear "witch hat" "black" "green">><<handheldwear "broomstick">><<feetwear "witch shoes" "black">>
	You nod your head. "Great!" Gwylan exclaims, grabbing you by the wrist and pulling you closer.
	<br><br>

	<<He>> twirls you around, <span class="lewd">dextrously stripping your clothes with ease</span>. It almost feels like they're floating away. <<His>> hands intrude on your more sensitive spots as <<he>> lifts one of your legs, then the other. Before you know it, you're entirely naked. <<arousal 800>><<garousal>>
	<br><br>

	Finally, <<he>> pulls the dress down over you. A witch hat is dropped on your head to complete the look, briefly obscuring your vision. You lift it to see Gwylan inspecting you, <<his>> hand to <<his>> chin.
<</if>>
<br><br>

"One moment." <<He>> disappears behind a shelf, and returns with a broom. <<He>> puts it in your hands, before vanishing once again, this time through a dark doorway.
You hear something scraping against wood. A moment later, <<he>> drags a cauldron into the room. "Here, use this."
<br><br>

You spin the broom around and stick the end into the cauldron, doing your best to look mischievous. Gwylan smiles. "Perfect, you look ready to put a hex on me. Next, the coat."
<<He>> grips your wrist again, grabbing the jacket of the vampire costume with <<his>> other hand.
<br><br>

<<switch $speech_attitude>>
	<<case "meek">>
		"W-wait, I thought you were just checking the fit!" you say.
	<<case "bratty">>
		"Hey, you said you were just checking the fit," you say.
	<<default>>
		"Wait," you start, "I thought you said you were just checking the fit."
<</switch>>
<br><br>

"Might as well check them all while we're here!" <<he>> says with a laugh.
<br><br>

<<link [[Next|Gwylan Talk Clothes Halloween 3]]>><</link>>
<br>

