:: Gwylan Talk Clothes Halloween 4
<<effects>><<set _tf to checkTFparts()>><<run statusCheck("Gwylan")>>

<<if $phase is 1>>
	<<if _tf.fallenAngelWings or _tf.demonWings>>
		You oustretch your arms and flap your wings, doing your best impression of a terror of the night. Gwylan claps. "Very scary, you're a natural!"
	<<elseif _tf.angelWings or _tf.birdWings>>
		You oustretch your arms and flap your wings, doing your best impression of a terror of the night. It's a little off because of your feathers, but Gwylan claps. "Very scary, you're a natural!"
	<<else>>
		You stretch your arms to your sides and start flapping them as if you were a bat. Gwylan giggles. "Good enough, I suppose."
	<</if>>
<<elseif $phase is 2>>
	You bend your fingers into a more intense grabbing gesture, and bare your
	<<if _tf.traitsFangs>>
		sharp fangs at Gwylan. "Yeah, just like..." <<He>> pauses, and leans in, getting a closer look at them. "Wow, those are pointy." <<He>> cups your cheek, and for a moment, you think <<hes>> going to try and feel them.
		<<He>> blushes and pulls <<his>> hand away. "Y-yeah, good job, very scary!" <<npcincr Gwylan lust 1>><<glust>>
	<<else>>
		teeth at Gwylan. "Yeah, just like that! Very scary."
	<</if>>
<<else>>
	You lick your <<if _tf.traitsFangs>>fangs<<else>>teeth<</if>> and lunge for Gwylan. <<He>> expects you to stop short. You don't.
	<br><br>

	You grab <<him>>, and
	<<if _tf.traitsFangs>>
		<<set $gwylanSeen.pushUnique("neck_bite")>>
		<span class="red">sink your fangs right into <<his>> neck</span>. <<He>> cries out and gasps.
		<br><br>

		<<if C.npc.Gwylan.lust gte 25>>
			<<He>> squirms, managing to shake you off before quickly getting low to the ground, as if <<he>> were about to pounce. <<He>> lunges and
			<<if _gwylanTF.fangs is "revealed">>
				<span class="red">bites you back with <<his>> own sharp fangs.</span> <<pain 7>><<ggpain>>
				<br><br>

				<<He>> withdraws and covers <<his>> mouth, blushing.
			<<elseif $hallucinations gte 2>>
				<<set $gwylanSeen.pushUnique("gwylan_fangs")>>
				<span class="lewd">bites you back</span>. <span class="red">Hard. You think you feel skin break.</span> <<pain 7>><<ggpain>>
				<br><br>

				<<He>> withdraws. <span class="lewd">For a moment, <<his>> teeth appear sharp, much like yours.</span> <<He>> blushes, covering <<his>> mouth.
			<<else>>
				<span class="lewd">bites you back</span>. It's not nearly as hard as you did, but it still hurts. <<pain 3>><<ggpain>>
				<br><br>

				<<He>> withdraws, covering <<his>> mouth and blushing.
			<</if>>
			<<if _gwylanTF.known>>
				"Sorry. Instincts."
			<<else>>
				"S-sorry, I don't know what came over me!"
			<</if>>
			<br><br>

			The two of you stand in silence for a moment, before <<he>> retreats behind a counter. <<He>> ducks down, re-emerging with some damp alcohol wipes.
			<<He>> gingerly cleans the bite marks <<he>> left on you, before doing the same to the ones you left on <<him>>. <<npcincr Gwylan lust 6>><<gglust>>
		<<else>>
			After a moment's hesitation, <<he>> lightly smacks you on the top of your head. "Could you please let go?"
			<br><br>

			You pull away, licking <<his>> blood off of your fangs suggestively. <<His>> face is bright red. <<He>> quickly bends behind a counter and produces a small hand mirror, inspecting the wound you just left. <<He>> runs <<his>> fingers over the red pinpricks and exhales. <<npcincr Gwylan lust 3>><<glust>>
		<</if>>
	<<else>>
		<span class="lewd">bite <<him>> on the neck</span>. <<He>> yips in surprise, but doesn't push you away.
		<br><br>

		After a moment's hesitation, <<he>> lightly smacks you on the top of your head. "Could you please let go?"
		<br><br>

		You pull away. <<He>> quickly bends behind a counter and produces a small hand mirror, inspecting <<his>> neck. You left a mark. <<He>> runs <<his>> fingers over it.
	<</if>>
	<br><br>

	<<He>> reaches up for a shelf, and pulls down a dark green scarf, wrapping it around <<his>> neck. "I suppose I asked for that." <<He>> fails to make eye contact with you initially, but shakes it off.
	<<His>> face is no less red, though. "L-let's just move on."
<</if>>
<br><br>

Before you can protest, <<he>> twirls you again, stripping you naked once more.
<br><br>

<<link [[Next|Gwylan Talk Clothes Halloween 5]]>><</link>>
