:: Gwylan Talk Clothes Scarecrow 2
<<effects>><<run statusCheck("Gwylan")>>
<<set $gwylanTalked.pushUnique("scarecrow")>>

<<if $phase is 1>>
	You tell Gwylan that it started appearing alongside the rest of the Halloween costumes. <<He>> nods, as if expecting that answer.
<<else>>
	<<set $gwylanSeen.pushUnique("farm_defended")>>
	You tell Gwylan that you started seeing it after you thoroughly thrashed Remy's attempts to burn down your farm. You tell <<him>> the whole story in great detail, about how each team was defeated through might and guile, and how the farm came out unscathed.
	<<if $wraith?.seenFarm>>
		You even mention the pale stranger that joined in.
	<</if>>
	<br><br>

	Gwylan listens with bated breath. <<He>> seems very invested, brightening up when you mention your triumphs, looking sullen when things seem grim, and
	<<if $wraith?.seenFarm>>
		becoming quite confused when you mention the pale figure.
	<<else>>
		gasping at every twist.
	<</if>>
	However, when you mention Remy by name, <<his>> face becomes hard to read.
	<br><br>

	"You punch far above your weight class," <<he>> finally says. "It makes sense. You were like a scarecrow, warding against the people trying to take something important from you. I bet the mere sight of you will make them think twice from now on."
<</if>>
<br><br>

<<endevent>><<npc Gwylan>><<person1>>
<<gwylanOptions>>

