:: Gwylan Talk Clothes Skeleton 2
<<effects>><<run statusCheck("Gwylan")>>
<<set $gwylanTalked.pushUnique("skeleton")>>

<<if $phase is 1>>
	You tell Gwylan that it started appearing alongside the rest of the Halloween costumes. <<He>> nods, as if expecting that answer.
<<else>>
	You tell Gwylan that it started appearing after you discovered the crypt below the old churchyard. <<He>> puts <<his>> hand to <<his>> chin and nods along as you explain.
	<br><br>

	"That makes sense. There's a lot of skeletons around there, although it's rarely used these days. The temple mostly cremates their dead, but even so, they used to bury the ashes, and there were some who preferred to be buried whole.
	Now, that whole area has been left to rot. Although, when I have free time, I like to visit and keep the dearly departed company." <<He>> starts to pace back and forth as <<he>> continues.
	<br><br>

	/* ToDo: Gwylan - Gwylan spends time at the churchyard once or twice a week */

	"It's possible that the underground portion used to be more directly connected to the temple itself, or somewhere else. Perhaps a collapse cut it off. Or perhaps the cloister is simply too busy to tend to their dead." <<He>> looks up.
	"They certainly have their hands full these days. The world has changed."
<</if>>
<br><br>

<<endevent>><<npc Gwylan>><<person1>>
