<<effects>><<run statusCheck("Gwylan")>>
You ask Gwylan about the Christmas costumes.
<br><br>

"Red and white are a great combination any time of the year," <<he>> starts, "but I have mixed feelings about stocking these." <<He>> stares at you for a moment, seemingly waiting for you to respond. "Get it? Stocking?"
<br><br>

<<He>> runs <<his>> hands along the Christmas hat, seeming to take comfort in the soft material. "Every season, someone tries to strike up a conversation with me about how it's actually a pagan holiday, as if it's not common knowledge."
