:: Gwylan Talk Clothes Christmas 2
<<effects>><<run statusCheck("Gwylan")>>
<<set $gwylanTalked.pushUnique("christmas")>>

<<if $phase is 1>>
	You tell Gwylan that they appeared around Christmas. <<He>> nods, as if expecting that answer.
<<else>>
	<<set $gwylanSeen.pushUnique("christmas_generosity")>>
	<<set $daily.gwylan.traumaTalk to true>>
	<<switch $speech_attitude>>
		<<case "meek">>
			"I... found these here after I left some money for a family in need," you say. "W-well, it was more than some. It was a lot. I think they needed it more than I did. They barely even had beds, I couldn't steal from them."
		<<case "bratty">>
			"I found these after I committed a reverse-robbery," you say. "I went in expecting to steal something, but I just... couldn't. They had nothing. They needed the money more than I did."
		<<default>>
			"I found these after I left money for a house I intended to steal from," you say. "They definitely needed it more than me."
	<</switch>>
	<br><br>

	Gwylan snickers. "What are you, Robin Hood? That's very noble of you.
	<<if $gwylanSeen.includesAny("caught", "caught_no_lewd")>>
		Why didn't you leave anything for me when you snuck in here?" <<He>> gives you a playful smile. "Only joking. If you did, I probably wouldn't ever find it."
	<<else>>
		Feel free to leave something behind for me too, if you ever break into the shop." <<He>> gives you a playful smile. "Only joking. If I caught you breaking in... well, never mind that."
	<</if>>
<</if>>
<br><br>

<<endevent>><<npc Gwylan>><<person1>>
<<gwylanOptions>>

