		<<case "bratty">>
			"Quit being so dramatic. You've got someone who loves you standing right here."
		<<default>>
			"I love you, even if you're just as prickly as that rose."
	<</switch>>
	<br><br>

	<<He>> winces. "Stop using that word. It's not something I can return, and it's wasted on me." <<He>> looks down, refusing to look at you.
