	<</switch>>
	<<His>> teeth clench, but you don't stop. "It won't last forever, so we just have to enjoy the time we do have, remember?"
	<br><br>

	"You can't understand," <<he>> says, <<his>> gaze turning dark. "I'm sorry that I've inflicted these feelings upon you."
	<<He>> slips <<his>> wrists free from your grip, and returns to the counter. "Put this out of your mind, dear."
<</if>>
