		"You still carry a burden. <<if !_tf.cowEars>>You were trying to hide it. <</if>>If it bothers you... <span class="blue">I can help you come to peace with this expression of your inner self</span>."
	<<else>>
		"Don't forget my offer. I can help you come to peace with this expression of your inner self."
	<</if>>
	<br><br>
<</if>>

<<gwylanOptions>>

