<<set $gwylanTalked.pushUnique("loincloth")>><<set $gwylan.progress += 2>>
<<set $daily.gwylan.traumaTalk to true>>
You tell Gwylan about your time with the wolf pack, from when the Black Wolf stole you away to becoming a member.
<br><br>

<<if _tf.wolfEars>>
	<<His>> eyes lock on your wolf ears.
<</if>>
<<if $gwylanSeen.includes("likes_wolves")>>
	"You've told me all about how much you like the wolves," <<he>> says with a giggle. "It's cute. I think you fit in with the forest pretty well."
<<else>>
	<<He>> looks fascinated by what you're saying. "So you like acting like a wolf?" <<he>> asks with a wide smile.
	<<if $gwylanSeen.includes("caught")>>
