:: Gwylan Talk Clothes Bird
<<effects>><<run statusCheck("Gwylan")>><<set _tf to checkTFparts()>><<set $daily.gwylan.clothesTalk++>>
<<set $gwylanTalked.pushUnique("bird")>><<set $gwylan.progress++>>
<<set $daily.gwylan.traumaTalk to true>>
<<if ($settings.monsterChance gte random(1, 100) and ($hallucinations gte 1 or !$settings.monsterHallucinationsOnly)) or $greathawkmonster is 2>><<set _hawkmonster to 1>><</if>>
You show Gwylan the feathery accessories.
<br><br>

<<His>> eyes go wide. "Oh, wow! Those are pristine! Let me see, let me see!" <<He>> grabs for them, and you hand them over.
<br><br>

"Such a waste to wear them like this," <<he>> says, thumbing the feathers. "These would be great in..." <<He>> looks up to you. "I must know how you got the shop to show these to you. If I found them first, they wouldn't be for sale."
<br><br>

You explain your time in the castle, and with the Great Hawk.
You realise that you're probably making <<if _hawkmonster is 1>><<nnpc_him "Great Hawk">><<else>>it<</if>> sound a lot more terrifying than <<if _hawkmonster is 1>><<nnpc_he "Great Hawk">><<else>>it<</if>> actually is, but you also realise that that's probably how <<if _hawkmonster is 1>><<nnpc_he "Great Hawk">><<else>>it<</if>> would want to be described.
<br><br>

"So, they're finally returning after all," Gwylan muses. "I thought the sightings were falsified. Wonderful. Wonderful!" <<Hes>> practically jumping up and down with excitement. "I'll have to plan a trip out to the moor. I'll need to make sure I can get close enough, and..."
<br><br>

<<He>> suddenly stops, and looks at you. "Hmm. In fact, I could use your help. You said you're already close with the <<if _hawkmonster is 1>>harpy<<else>>hawk<</if>> that controls the tower. <span class="blue">I may request that you bring me some of <<if _hawkmonster is 1>><<nnpc_his "Great Hawk">><<else>>its<</if>> feathers, next time I need a favour.</span>"
<<if $harpy gte 6>>
	<<set $gwylanSeen.pushUnique("preen")>>
	<<if _tf.birdWings>>
		<<He>> takes a moment to look at your wings. <<He>> walks around you, and runs <<his>> hands along them.
	<<else>>
		<<He>> walks around you, and you <span class="pink">feel <<him>> run <<his>> hands along your wings.</span> You were sure that they were hidden.
	<</if>>
	<<if $birdFly>>
		"Fascinating hybridisation. I could make use of these, too. If you don't mind, I would really like to... preen you." <<He>> blushes.
	<<else>>
		"Fascinating hybridisation, but the feathers are virgin. Untested. You haven't flown with these yet. If they ever become strong enough for flight, and if you don't mind, I would really like to... preen you." <<He>> blushes.
	<</if>>
	<<if $gwylanSeen.includes("hypnosis_peace")>>
		"I hope I was able to help you come to peace with these."
	<<elseif !$gwylanSeen.includes("player_tf")>>
		<<set $gwylanSeen.pushUnique("player_tf")>>
		"If you <span class="blue">begin to doubt or resent these expressions of your inner self</span>, I know how to help."
	<<else>>
		"Don't forget my offer. I can help if you begin to doubt these expressions of your inner self."
	<</if>>
<<else>>
	<<He>> stands on the tips of <<his>> toes, as if looking for something behind you.
<</if>>
<br><br>

<<He>> continues beaming at the feathers for some time.
<br><br>

<<gwylanOptions>>

:: Gwylan Talk Clothes Prison
<<effects>><<run statusCheck("Gwylan")>><<set _tf to checkTFparts()>><<set $daily.gwylan.clothesTalk++>>
<<set $gwylanTalked.pushUnique("prison")>><<set $gwylan.progress += 2>>
<<set _prisonStats to V.badEndStats.find(stat => stat.source === "Prison")>>
<<set $daily.gwylan.traumaTalk to true>>
당신은 그윌란에게 죄수복을 보여준다.
<br><br>

"감옥 섬에 다녀왔구나," 그는 당신이 설명하기도 전에 말한다. "뻔하지. 네 눈빛을 보면 알아. 어떻게 탈출한 거야?"
<br><br>

그는 당신이 주저하는 것을 알아차린다. "걱정 마, 누구에게도 말하지 않을게," 그는 윙크하며 미소 짓는다.
<br><br>

<<if ["prisonWren", "prisonWrenKylar"].includes(_prisonStats?.reasonEnd)>>
	"친구가 섬에서 몰래 빼내 줬어요," 당신은 설명한다. "많은 사람들의 조력이 필요했죠."
	<br><br>

	그는 끄덕인다. "그런 장소에서는, 조력이 돈 이상의 가치를 갖지. 장담할 수 있어."
<<elseif _prisonStats?.reasonEnd is "prisonSwimming">>
	"I had to make some friends and cause some distractions," you explain. "Until I was able to swim away without notice. I swam all the way back to the mainland."
	<br><br>

	<<He>> looks surprised. "That's incredibly dangerous. You're lucky, the ocean must have been favouring you. Such a distance... you could have been swept away!" <<He>> suddenly hugs you. "Don't be so reckless! I am glad you came back, though."
<<elseif _prisonStats?.reasonEnd is "escapedSoaring">>
	"I befriended the giant birds that watched over the prison, and flew," you explain.
	<br><br>

	<<if _tf.birdWings>>
		<<He>> takes a moment to look at your wings. "You flew. Of course. I can't think of a better way myself."
	<<else>>
		<<He>> blinks at you. "You... flew. You're a fascinating one, you know? I don't think you're lying to me, despite such a strange claim."
	<</if>>
<<elseif _prisonStats?.reasonEnd is "prisonRut">>
	"I don't remember all of it," you explain. "There was a punishment, something about damnation. They threw me into the rut. I don't know how long I was down there, but I saw things. Insects feasting on something."
	<br><br>

	Gwylan listens intently, waiting for you to continue, but you have nothing more to say.
<<else>>
	"I simply served my time," you say.
	<br><br>

	Gwylan nods. "Did the punishment match your crimes? I suppose it doesn't matter. I'm glad you're back."
<</if>>
<br><br>

<<gwylanOptions>>

:: Gwylan Talk Clothes Asylum
<<effects>><<run statusCheck("Gwylan")>><<set $daily.gwylan.clothesTalk++>>
<<set $gwylanTalked.pushUnique("asylum")>><<set $gwylan.progress += 3>>
<<set _asylumStats to V.badEndStats.find(stat => stat.source === "Asylum")>>
<<tearup>><<hallucinogen 120>>
<<set $daily.gwylan.traumaTalk to true>>
You show Gwylan the straightjacket.
<br><br>

<<He>> freezes up, but only for a moment. "That's not something I would ever stock," <<he>> says. "Even if it's a replica."
<br><br>

You tell <<him>> about your time at the asylum. <<He>> looks more and more upset as you explain everything you can remember. Much of it you wouldn't share willingly, but for some reason, you find it hard to stop.
<br><br>

Gwylan holds up a hand to stop you, and wipes a tear from your eye. You're not sure when that started. Why are you crying?
<br><br>

Suddenly, you're being hugged tightly. "Thank you for telling me," <<he>> says. "I know it's not easy to do, when you've been told that none of it is real, or that it was all your fault."
<<His>> embrace tightens. "I believe you. I promise. Even if no one else does, I do."
<br><br>

<<if $gwylanSeen.includes("hypnosis_removal_suggestion")>>
	<<He>> pulls away, and holds a finger to your forehead. "Remember. If <<nnpc_he "Harper">> still lingers in your mind, or if you're overcome with urges that you know are not your own, tell me. I can help you."
<<else>>
	<<He>> pulls away, and holds a finger to your forehead. "If <<nnpc_he "Harper">> still lingers in your mind, or if you're <span class="blue">overcome with urges that you know are not your own</span>, tell me. I can help you."
<</if>>
<br><br>

<<He>> gives you a warm smile. "These burdens are meant to be shared, not suppressed. If everyone kept it all to themselves, there'd be no more stories to tell."
<br><br>

<<gwylanOptions>>

<!-- Temple -->

:: Gwylan Talk Clothes Temple
<<effects>><<run statusCheck("Gwylan")>>
<<set $gwylanTalked.pushUnique("temple")>>
You walk around the shop with Gwylan, browsing all the religious attire.
<br><br>

<<switch $speech_attitude>>
	<<case "meek">>
		"Wh-why do you have all of these, anyways?" you ask.
	<<case "bratty">>
		"So, why do you stock all these?" you ask.
	<<default>>
		"Why do you stock so many of the temple's clothes?" you ask.
<</switch>>
<br><br>

Gwylan ponders for a moment. "Good business." <<He>> shrugs. "They burn through a lot of clothing. Must be a..." <<He>> pauses for a moment. "Physical job."
<br><br>

You decide not to ask any more questions.
<br><br>

<<He>> looks around at all of the different outfits. A shadow passes over <<his>> face. <<He>> turns to you with <<= V.gwylanSeen.includes("yearning") ? "distress" : _gwylanLovePercent gte 75 ? "concern" : "a troubled frown">>, and clasps your hands in <<his>> own. "You are a pure, shining soul, dear. Don't let anyone swallow your light and claim it as their own."
<br><br>

<<gwylanOptions>>

