:: Gwylan Talk Clothes Temple Monk and Nun
<<effects>><<run statusCheck("Gwylan")>><<set $daily.gwylan.clothesTalk++>>
<<set $gwylanTalked.pushUnique("temple_monk_and_nun")>>
You show Gwylan the monk and nun robes.
<br><br>

"These aren't official, but the cloister doesn't seem to mind. They make adjustments on these rather than making their own from scratch." <<He>> smiles at you. "It's fascinating how they pick and choose what is allowed and what isn't."
<br><br>

<<He>> pauses for a moment. "So, you're moving up in rank with them. What exactly did you do to earn it?"
<br><br>

"I'm not sure I'm supposed to share," you start. "There was a trial. It was tough, and I saw something at the end." You shiver as the memory resurfaces.
<br><br>

<<He>> places a hand on your shoulder. "It's hard to unsee, isn't it? Once you see the cracks, the holes, you start to see them everywhere."
<br><br>

<<He>> stops, seeming unsure how to follow up that comment. "Is Jordan doing well?"
<br><br>

You nod, which prompts Gwylan to smile a little wider.
<br><br>

<<gwylanOptions>>

