:: Gwylan Talk Clothes Temple Confessor
<<effects>><<run statusCheck("Gwylan")>><<set $daily.gwylan.clothesTalk++>>
<<set $gwylanTalked.pushUnique("temple_confessor")>><<set $gwylan.progress += 2>>
You show Gwylan the confessor's robes and habit.
<br><br>

<<He>> tilts <<his>> head.
<<if $gwylanSeen.includes("ritual_beast")>>
	"The confessors do something similar to what we do. Their methods are... different, though. Often cruel."
<<else>>
	"The confessors do ugly work, and it's often cruel. Stitching up holes in the world, even when it leads to terrible suffering."
<</if>>
<<He>> looks right in your eyes. "You've gotten involved with them, haven't you?"
<br><br>

You explain how you met the Bishop. Gwylan listens intently to all of it, but you can't shake the feeling that you're not telling <<him>> anything <<he>> doesn't already know.
<br><br>

"Don't overextend yourself," <<he>> cautions. <<if $gwylanSeen.includes("ritual_beast")>>"Healing the world can leave holes in yourself."<<else>>"Wings that shield may smother just as easily."<</if>>
<br><br>

You promise to take care. It seems to mollify <<him>> as much as any empty words can.
<br><br>

<<gwylanOptions>>

:: Gwylan Talk Clothes Temple Exorcist
<<effects>><<run statusCheck("Gwylan")>><<set $daily.gwylan.clothesTalk++>>
<<set $gwylanTalked.pushUnique("temple_exorcist")>><<set $gwylan.progress++>>
You ask Gwylan about the exorcist's uniform. <<He>> shakes <<his>> head. "It's not a real one. Look." <<He>> takes it from you, and points at the collar.
<br><br>

"The temple takes these things very seriously, so each ordained exorcist's uniform is numbered. It would be right here." <<He>> opens the collar, and <<his>> face turns pale at what <<he>> sees. <<He>> quickly hands it back to you. "How did you find this?"
<br><br>

You explain everything. The dance job, the missing member of Jordan's flock, and the ritual you interrupted. Gwylan becomes more and more solemn as your story progresses.
<br><br>

"You did a very good thing," <<he>> says. "I can see why this one has a number now. The shop thinks you've earned it."
<br><br>

<<gwylanOptions>>

