:: Gwylan Talk Clothes Chef Cream
<<effects>><<run statusCheck("Gwylan")>>
<<if $phase is 1 or $phase is 2 and $hypnosis_traits.devotion gte 1 and !$willpowerSuccess>>
	<<set $gwylanSeen.pushUnique("cafe_chef_truth")>>
	<<if $phase is 2 and $hypnosis_traits.devotion gte 1 and !$willpowerSuccess>>
		You try to keep yourself quiet. <span class="red">You feel scolding disappointment wash over you, despite Gwylan's continued smile.</span>
		You can't help it. <span class="red">You tell <<him>> everything.</span> <<stress 6>><<gstress>>
	<<else>>
		You tell Gwylan that the key is in the cream, and exactly how you make it.
	<</if>>
	<br><br>

	<<if $gwylanSeen.includes("player_fluids_taste") and !$gwylanSeen.includes("player_fluids_realisation")>>
		<<set $gwylanSeen.pushUnique("player_fluids_realisation")>>
		<<He>> listens closely, <<his>> smile gradually fading into a look of realisation.
		"So that's why you taste so familiar," <<he>> says.
	<<else>>
		<<He>> listens closely, <<his>> smile gradually fading into an expression of pondering.
	<</if>>
	"Fascinating. Using your own bodily fluids." <<He>> starts to grill you for more details, such as your diet and any medications you take.
	<br><br>

	<<He>> gives you a satisfied smile when <<hes>> done.
	<<if C.npc.Gwylan.dom gte 15>>
		"<<pcPetname "Gwylan" "good">>, being so honest with me," <<he>> says, patting you on the head.
		<<if $hypnosis_traits.devotion gte 1>>
			<span class="witchbloom">It fills you with bliss.</span> <<stress -6>><<trauma -6>><<lstress>><<ltrauma>>
			<br><br>
		<</if>>
	<<else>>
		"Thank you. Your secret is safe with me." <<He>> pats you on the head.
	<</if>>
	<span class="pink">"I may ask you for a sample in the future."</span> <<arousal 500>><<garousal>>
<<else>>
	<<if $hypnosis_traits.devotion gte 1>>
		<span class="green">You block out the compulsion.</span>
	<</if>>
	<<switch $speech_attitude>>
		<<case "meek">>
			"I-I can't tell," you say. "It's a secret recipe."
		<<case "bratty">>
			"I'm not giving my secret recipe away for anyone," you say, crossing your arms. "It's nothing personal."
		<<default>>
			"You're right, it's a secret. I can't reveal it," you say.
	<</switch>>
	<br><br>

	Gwylan pouts. "Very well. I'll squeeze it out of you one day." <<His>> choice of words makes you wonder if <<he>> already knows, and just wanted to hear you say it.
<</if>>
<br><br>

