	<<case "bratty">>
		"Because latex is hot and shows off my goods. Next question." You grin and stick your tongue out at Gwylan.
	<<default>>
		"It's skintight and highlights my figure. What's not to like?" You wink at Gwylan.
<</switch>>
You illustrate the point by running your hands down your body and
<<if $player.perceived_breastsize gte 4>>
	cupping your <<breasts>>.
<<elseif calculatePenisBulge() gte 4>>
	grabbing your bulge.
<<elseif $player.perceived_bottomsize gte 4>>
	squeezing your <<bottom>>.
<<else>>
	emphasising your form.
<</if>>
<br><br>

Gwylan snickers. <<He>> straightens up and surveys you with a studious look, tapping <<his>> chin in mock contemplation.
<<if $worn.upper.name is "catsuit" and $worn.lower.name is "catsuit bottoms">>
	"Yes, yes, I can see how it accentuates your assets. A worthy investment indeed."
<<else>>
	"Yes, of course, I can only imagine how it accentuates your assets. You must give me a visual demonstration sometime."
<</if>>
<<He>> drops the overly-formal tone and gives you a playful smile.
<br><br>

<<link [[Next|Gwylan Talk Clothes Catsuit 2]]>><</link>>
