:: Gwylan Talk Clothes Catsuit Useful
<<effects>><<run statusCheck("Gwylan")>><<set _tf to checkTFparts()>>
"I just thought it would come in handy," you say.
<br><br>

"Fair enough," Gwylan says with a nod. "It's easier to skulk around at night if you blend in the darkness. If nothing else, dressing like the person you want to be can boost the confidence. I'm sure it's proved useful."
<<if _tf.foxTail or _tf.foxEars>>
	<<He>> looks at your <<= _tf.foxEars ? "fox ears" : "fox tail">>. "Very useful, I imagine."
	<<if _gwylanTF.known>>
		<<He>> gives you a knowing smile, tail swishing gently.
	<<else>>
		<<His>> smile is genuine.
	<</if>>
<</if>>
<br><br>

