:: Gwylan Talk Clothes Catsuit 2
<<effects>><<run statusCheck("Gwylan")>>
<<if $phase is "free">>
	"No special reason," you say. "I just like getting free clothes."
	<br><br>

	Gwylan giggles. "As valid a reason as any. Though I'll admit I'd hoped for a bit more to the story."
	<br><br>

	You try to think of a more interesting detail to share. "Oh, there is one other thing," you add,
<<elseif $phase isnot "wren">>
	"Plus," you add,
<</if>>
"I bumped into another person there.
<<switch $speech_attitude>>
	<<case "meek">>
		When I opened the container... there was someone else inside. With a gun."
	<<case "bratty">>
		When I broke into the container, I found myself staring down the barrel of a gun."
	<<default>>
		When I broke into the container, someone pointed a gun at me."
<</switch>>
<br><br>

Gwylan's eyes widen. "I assume it wasn't law enforcement, since you're here and not in prison."
<br><br>

You shake your head. "A smuggler. I'm not sure what <<nnpc_he "Wren">> was doing in there, or how <<nnpc_he "Wren">> intended to get out. I hadn't really thought about it before, but <<nnpc_he "Wren">> was locked inside."
<br><br>

<<if $phase is "symbol">>
	Gwylan frowns. "Given the contents of the container <<nnpc_he "Wren">> was in, I'd say that's someone to be cautious around." <<He>> gives a light shrug. "But maybe I'm just being presumptuous."
<<else>>
	Gwylan smiles. "An unexpected surprise for the both of you, then." <<He>> giggles. "Do you think <<nnpc_he "Wren">> locked <<nnpc_himself "Wren">> in by mistake, then tried to play it cool when you gallantly rescued <<nnpc_him "Wren">>?"
<</if>>
<br><br>

"<<nnpc_He "Wren">> was secretive, for sure. <<nnpc_He "Wren">> said that catsuit looked like it would fit me, so I decided to take it."
<br><br>

"I'm sure the intended recipient didn't miss it," Gwylan says with a mischievous smile. "Thanks for sharing. <<= $gwylanTalked.length gte 5 ? "You always have the most interesting adventures" : "That was quite the adventure">>. You'll have to tell me if you go on any other daring exploits of larceny and espionage, now that you have the right getup."
<br><br>

<<if $bird?.hunts?.estate is "complete" and !$gwylanTalked.includes("heist_silver")>>
	<<link [[Tell Gwylan about the silver bar you stole|Gwylan Talk Clothes Catsuit 3]]>><<set $phase2 to "silver">><</link>>
	<br>
<</if>>
<<if $lakestealgold is 1 and !$gwylanTalked.includes("heist_gold")>>
	<<link [[Tell Gwylan about the gold bar you stole|Gwylan Talk Clothes Catsuit 3]]>><<set $phase2 to "gold">><</link>>
	<br>
<</if>>
<<if $wrenHeist or $wrenSeen?.includes("heist") and !$gwylanTalked.includes("heist_wren")>>
	<<link [[Tell Gwylan about the heist with Wren|Gwylan Talk Clothes Catsuit 3]]>><<set $phase2 to "heist">><</link>>
	<br>
<</if>>
<<link [[Thank Gwylan for listening|Gwylan Talk Clothes Catsuit 3]]>><<set $phase2 to "thank">><</link>>
<br>

:: Gwylan Talk Clothes Catsuit 3
<<effects>><<run statusCheck("Gwylan")>>

<<if $phase2 is "silver">>
	"Outfit aside, I have been on an adventure of larceny and espionage..."

	<<include "Gwylan Talk Heist Silver">>
<<elseif $phase2 is "gold">>
	/* Kirsty: Yes this is unreachable. Yes, it makes me laugh. Missing quote in "bratty" and default cases is intentional, as the sentence continues in :: Gwylan Talk Heist Gold */
	<<switch $speech_attitude>>
		<<case "meek">>
			"It's not my most interesting experience stealing," you say.
		<<case "bratty">>
			"If you thought that was interesting, you ain't seen nothing yet.
		<<default>>
			"That wasn't even my most interesting experience stealing.
	<</switch>>

	<<include "Gwylan Talk Heist Gold">>
<<elseif $phase2 is "heist">>
	"Wait, it gets even better," you say.

	<<include "Gwylan Talk Heist Wren">>
<<else>>
	Gwylan looks surprised. "You don't need to thank me. I'm always happy to listen."
<</if>>
<br><br>

<<He>> stands up. "In any case, I appreciate you sharing all this. And it's good to know that you're in the business of sneaking around. I'll make sure to change my locks." <<He>> smiles.
<br><br>

<<endevent>><<npc Gwylan>><<person1>>
<<gwylanOptions>>

:: Gwylan Talk Heist Silver
<<effects>><<run statusCheck("Gwylan")>>
<<set $gwylanTalked.pushUnique("heist_silver")>>

You recount the tale of your grandest hunt, reliving all the narrow brushes with guards and close calls with lurkers. You talk about the pulse of adrenaline as you crept closer to the mysterious light, of weaponising caged lurkers, of the satisfaction felt when your hand finally closed around the Lure. You tell Gwylan about the giant lurker, your daring escape, and the intricate seal carved into its base. <<He>> listens intently, gasping at all the right moments. When you finally finish talking, you're breathless.
<br><br>

Gwylan claps. "Wow! I felt like I was there with you. Very well told!" <<His>> smile dims, as <<he>> suddenly grows serious. "That silver bar, and the pattern etched in it, could have had devastating consequences if left with those people. Some say that silver's a sacred metal, capable of keeping evil at bay. Pure. Holy. Binding. But it can also be used to commit atrocities in the name of belief. It's all in who wields it. I'm glad you were able to take it. Wield it well, or better yet: not at all. It sounds like you've found a safe home for it."

:: Gwylan Talk Heist Gold
<<effects>><<run statusCheck("Gwylan")>>
<<set $gwylanTalked.pushUnique("heist_gold")>>

<<switch $speech_attitude>>
	<<case "meek">>
		"I found a gold bar once. And I took it by, um, well..." Gwylan has to lean in to hear you whisper, "...putting it up my..." You're unable to finish the sentence, and simply point to your unmentionables.
	<<case "bratty">>
		One time I stole a gold bar by shoving it up my <<= $player.vaginaExist ? "cunt" : "ass">>," you say plainly. <<if !$player.vaginaExist>>"Gotta say, I get why buttplugs have flared bases now."<</if>>
	<<default>>
		I once stole a gold bar by storing it in nature's pocket," you say.
<</switch>>
<br><br>

Gwylan opens <<his>> mouth, then closes it again. "Well," <<he>> finally says. "To each <<pher>> own methods!" <<His>> face is bright red.

