<<if $wrenHeist and Time.hour gt 20 and !$wrenHeistDance.attended>>
	"I have a heist planned for tonight. With that person." You trail off at the realisation that <span class="red">you've stood Wren up</span>. "Or I did, at least."
	<br><br>

	Gwylan's eyebrows raise. "Lost track of time? I assume a lot has changed between you two. Hopefully <<nnpc_hes "Wren">> the understanding sort." <<He>> pats you on the head.
<<else>>
	"I <<= $wrenHeist and !$wrenHeistDance.attended ? "have a heist planned for tonight" : "went on a heist">> with the same person who pointed that gun at me."
	<<if $wrenHeist and !$wrenHeistDance.attended>>
		<<if Time.hour gte 19>>
			You check the time and jump to your feet. "Right now, in fact."
		<</if>>
