:: Gwylan Talk Heists Share
<<effects>><<run statusCheck("Gwylan")>>

<<switch $phase>>
	<<case "gold">>
		/* Kirsty: Yes this is unreachable. Yes, it makes me laugh. Missing quote in "bratty" and default cases is intentional, as the sentence continues in :: Gwylan Talk Heist Gold */
		<<switch $speech_attitude>>
			<<case "meek">>
				"This is a bit embarrassing to admit, but I... I trust you," you begin. You can feel the heat rising to your cheeks.
			<<case "bratty">>
				You lean in conspiratorially. "You'll get a kick out of this one, I'm sure.
			<<default>>
				"It's kind of a funny story, really.
		<</switch>>
		<<include "Gwylan Talk Heist Gold">>

