"Dignified," <<he>> says. "How did you find this?"
<br><br>

<<switch $speech_attitude>>
	<<case "meek">>
		"I... I got lost in a story," you say. "It felt like the book pulled me in, and I felt everything like it was really happening to me. Then I found this dress here."
	<<case "bratty">>
