You show Gwylan the various flowers around the shop. The roses, the daisies, the flower crown, and the ones on <<his>> hat.
<br><br>

"Isn't it wonderful how these flowers never wilt? The ones that find their way into the shop only rot when discarded," <<he>> says proudly. "Roses are my favourite, but this crown is cute too."
<br><br>

<<switch $speech_attitude>>
