<<He>> smiles at you. "It takes a practised hand to weave together something so delicate without ruining the petals. I have more around here somewhere."
<<He>> starts rummaging around the shop, and returns with a collection of many different flowers. The smell of all of them together is overpowering, but pleasant. <<hallucinogen 20>><<ghallucinogens>>
<br><br>

You recognise most of them, but there's three that stick out from the rest. Three closed purple bulbs, similar to tulips but longer, and... glowing?
